plot: Resentment surfaces between Slade and Jo on her birthday. Lauri and George take the entire family on a vacation to Maui, Hawaii where Lauri's son, Josh is missed. The entire Keough family is walking on eggshells when Shane invites a girl he met on the internet to come spend a couple of days with him. Meanwhile, Tammy's daughter Lindsey gets her driver's license and hopes for a luxury car and Vicki's patience is tested while she balances work and taking care of a new puppy.—Anonymous
